text: "Token Angels" was the lead single released by Australian recording artist Wendy Matthews' debut solo studio album, Émigré. The single was released on 3 September 1990. At the ARIA Music Awards of 1991, the song won Breakthrough Artist - Single award. Matthews subsequently included the song on her 1999 greatest hits album, Stepping Stones, and her 2007 compilation album, The Essential Wendy Matthews. == Track listing== # "Token Angels" - 4:53 # "Iroquois Lullaby" # "Fruit Bearing Tree" ==Charts== {|class="wikitable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center;" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (1990) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- !scope="row" |- |} ==References== Category:1990 singles Category:1990 songs Category:Wendy Matthews songs Category:ARIA Award-winning songs
